{"tid":1994463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"索帶 === 暴動?","createTime":"2020-04-29T13:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T01:24:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2c1aa1f5009252f4397cb4c6cd8afa9c3b775d33","tid":1994463,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89-11-2-%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3%E8%97%8F%E7%B4%A2%E5%B8%B6%E7%AD%89%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81-%E7%A9%BA%E5%A7%90%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E8%A3%BD%E7%89%87%E4%BA%BA%E7%AD%89-7-%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589-11-2-%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E9%258A%2585%25E9%2591%25BC%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%2597%258F%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%2593%2581-%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%25A7%2590%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E7%2589%2587%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25AD%2589-7-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw69osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=44db3409\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589-11-2-%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E9%258A%2585%25E9%2591%25BC%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%2597%258F%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%2593%2581-%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%25A7%2590%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E7%2589%2587%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25AD%2589-7-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F&h=31d15aea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89-11-2-%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3%E8%97%8F%E7%B4%A2%E5%B8%B6%E7%AD%89%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81-%E7%A9%BA%E5%A7%90%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E8%A3%BD%E7%89%87%E4%BA%BA%E7%AD%89-7-%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涉 11.2 灣仔銅鑼灣藏索帶等物品 空姐及廣告製片人等 7 人准保釋<br />\n<br />\n去年 11 月 2 日，逾 120 名民主派區議會候選人在維園發起選舉聚會，惟活動遭腰斬，及後灣仔及銅鑼灣一帶發生嚴重警民衝突。7名男女，包括一名空姐、一名廣告製片及16歲女學生，被控在灣仔及銅鑼灣管有索帶等物品，事隔半年遭起訴，各面對一項「管有適合作非法用途的工具」罪，今日在東區裁判法院提訊，均准保釋。控方透露，不排除加控空姐及廣告製片暴動罪。<br />\n<br />\n各被告今日毋須答辯，案件分別押後至 6 月中旬及 7 月中旬再訊。其中，空姐及廣告製片人的案件押後，以待警方作進一步調查，控方在庭上透露，將會考慮加控二人及其他一同被補人士暴動罪。7 人均獲准以現金 1,000 至 3,000元保釋，除了空姐因工作需要獲准離港外，其餘被告不准離港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當「管有適合作非法用途的工具」好難砌得入既時候，班狗就用重罪去試告</span></strong>"},{"pid":"333c4684890fe8cd3d592c18ae26e3b0ff119551","tid":1994463,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"推比多d人睇?"},{"pid":"2ed7d2600768608390236a1555c385f2fa1ca947","tid":1994463,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:37:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b003309c875c5529c91d845e7bd141e41d38495c","tid":1994463,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:46:47.000Z","msg":"推大力d"},{"pid":"e25ac3140dd4f2c6caa833d7eac58db647535a2b","tid":1994463,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:05:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200429/s00001/1588161020042/%e9%9b%bb%e5%b7%a5%e6%b6%89%e7%ae%a1%e6%9c%89%e7%b4%a2%e5%b8%b6%e7%99%bd%e8%89%b2%e6%b2%b9%e7%8d%b2%e6%92%a4%e6%8e%a7%e5%85%bc%e7%8d%b2%e8%a8%9f%e8%b2%bb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200429%2Fs00001%2F1588161020042%2F%25e9%259b%25bb%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e6%25b6%2589%25e7%25ae%25a1%25e6%259c%2589%25e7%25b4%25a2%25e5%25b8%25b6%25e7%2599%25bd%25e8%2589%25b2%25e6%25b2%25b9%25e7%258d%25b2%25e6%2592%25a4%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2585%25bc%25e7%258d%25b2%25e8%25a8%259f%25e8%25b2%25bb&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw69osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=3c722c4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200429%2Fs00001%2F1588161020042%2F%25e9%259b%25bb%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e6%25b6%2589%25e7%25ae%25a1%25e6%259c%2589%25e7%25b4%25a2%25e5%25b8%25b6%25e7%2599%25bd%25e8%2589%25b2%25e6%25b2%25b9%25e7%258d%25b2%25e6%2592%25a4%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2585%25bc%25e7%258d%25b2%25e8%25a8%259f%25e8%25b2%25bb&h=b5aaf6b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200429/s00001/1588161020042/%e9%9b%bb%e5%b7%a5%e6%b6%89%e7%ae%a1%e6%9c%89%e7%b4%a2%e5%b8%b6%e7%99%bd%e8%89%b2%e6%b2%b9%e7%8d%b2%e6%92%a4%e6%8e%a7%e5%85%bc%e7%8d%b2%e8%a8%9f%e8%b2%bb</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>39歲電工於今年1月1日民陣元旦遊行被腰斬後，在銅鑼灣遭警方截查，涉在其袋內搜得索帶、汽球、白色油等物品，被控以一項管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途使用罪。控方今（29日）在東區裁判法院，以證據不足為由向裁判官申請撤控並獲批，被告訟費申請亦獲批。</strong><br />\n<br />\n辯方為報稱電工馮志強（39歲）申請訟費，但控方表示，他雖稱大部分物品為工作所用，但其實當日被告毋須工作，並在警誡下保持緘默，無解釋為何不用上班卻帶着工具，以及該些物品與其工作有何關連，認為他自招嫌疑。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>署理主任裁判官錢禮則指出，馮志強保持緘默是其權利，不構成自招嫌疑，因此批准辯方的訟費申請。</strong><br />\n<br />\n控罪原指稱馮志強在2020年1月1日，於銅鑼灣站E出口管有一包塑料索帶、一隻白色手套、一個黑色口罩、一包氣球及一樽白色油。"},{"pid":"cfb85a6a8b293e0a96f7bf97956762fa2142ea8d","tid":1994463,"uid":11916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:09:13.000Z","msg":"空姐手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf65a29387a33c384eba2106b7a72fa1be7d4aa0","tid":1994463,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:31:05.000Z","msg":"再推呀"},{"pid":"579f8daa700ba42757b142fdb7370b3677b51915","tid":1994463,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:31:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"071de1895ba270b8ae18374111f86d31f2f7ca72","tid":1994463,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"暴動好易入<br />\n你係現場出現就入得"},{"pid":"ed195ae354c6da3838e169f188e5292be65b9667","tid":1994463,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfb85a6a8b293e0a96f7bf97956762fa2142ea8d","tid":1994463,"uid":11916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:09:13.000Z","msg":"空姐手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8442eb54fe8f5157e3a9eb206131c30b087be2","tid":1994463,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:46:23.000Z","msg":"我經常放咗工、放假去宜家家私攞紙尺用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b847a7b8b86403f59ce1d70078491f308996e4a3","tid":1994463,"uid":5674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T17:24:12.000Z","msg":"枕頭可以焗死人<br />\n豆腐可以啃死人<br />\n<br />\n黑警無限釋法，無限上綱上線<br />\n「管有適合作非法用途的工具」，黑警想砌乜就砌乜"},{"pid":"570f14ec0a6252ee86218ab29ba4f9257e77625f","tid":1994463,"uid":23198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:24:34.000Z","msg":"推"}]}